LLDP Network Device Scanner – Code Brief\par
\par
\section{Project Overview}\par
This Windows application captures and displays Link Layer Discovery Protocol (LLDP) packets in real time via a Tkinter GUI. It uses Npcap (WinPcap‑API compatible mode) for packet sniffing and parses LLDP TLVs to show device information.\par
\par
